{"tid":1197380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】發動6.12罷工罷市！100毛CALL4VAN等多店響應","createTime":"2019-06-10T03:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T04:02:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19f95e193471c8f52836b4023603556a3ab6c1dc","tid":1197380,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190610/large/1560135255_a362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190610%2Flarge%2F1560135255_a362.jpg&h=17986d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府無視昨日103萬人上街反對＜逃犯條例＞修訂，強行按照原定計劃於本周三（6月12日）上立法會大會恢復二讀辯論，有網民將行動進一步升級，發動於6月12日罷市及罷課，多間公司店舖響應，包括100毛及CALL4VAN等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【引渡惡法●國際關注】歐洲美加華人接力聲援 BBC：97年主權移交後最大規模遊行<br />\n<br />\n100毛創辦人林日曦在facebook宣佈，6月12日公司將停運一天，同事毋須上班。他感嘆指，人大了常會想很多事情做了有沒有用，如反對、遊行、嗌救命等，「係，其實好似好多嘢都冇用，所以諗諗吓我都費事諗，我同我的拍擋決定，六月十二號公司停運一天」。他坦言，行動或許未有太大作用，「可能都係冇乜用，不過唔想諗，希望香港快啲好返」。<br />\n<br />\n電召貨車應用程式公司CALL4VAN亦在facebook宣佈，由6月12號起停止運作，並呼籲各商戶及員工加入罷市行列。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【引渡惡法】凌晨爆發流血衝突 警員持槍清場 多名示威者被捕<br />\n<br />\n「懸壺善學堂」凌晨亦在facebook發帖，宣佈今日至6月12日《逃犯條例》二讀前，由每位醫師及同事自由決定是否罷工。其中李家麟醫師今日會如期在診所照顧已預約的病人，「惟所有收入會另存作基金，不作私用，保證用作救助其他同路人」。至於其他醫師和姑娘是否上班，「本人不會指示亦不負責」。<br />\n<br />\n懸壺善學堂指，若診療等候時間受影響，「冤有頭債有主請出來向踐踏市民意願、危害各位安危的中國香港特區政府追究」，同時邀請各公司、機構、個人，勇於採取類似行動以回應，更稱會慎重考慮是否要短期內結束一切商業性之業務，「一起以hea爆共渡時艱」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，馳名小食店「渣哥」亦決定在6.12「拉閘停業」，罷市一天；大角嘴的小型咖啡店「Craft Coffee Roaster」都在facebook宣佈6.12罷市。<br />\n<br />\n罷市行動獲得不少網民支持，冀關鍵時候香港人能團結一致，共同反對惡法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190610/59697013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59697013&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e21cbfff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59697013&h=829045f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190610/59697013</a>"},{"pid":"042210fdf30a0eab5273d0eec47288cc2d01fb55","tid":1197380,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACfowuR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACfowuR.png&h=493310f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6月12日全港罷工罷課抗議香港定立逃犯惡法!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/620332871773292/?source=unknown\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F620332871773292%2F%3Fsource%3Dunknown&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=7be7264c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/620332871773292/?source=unknown</a>"},{"pid":"994510641a79b136548810a138a11b74c571fcb1","tid":1197380,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"達仔都罷台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec49bcf1460a59e08aeeb60be1de1c45dc79f5b3","tid":1197380,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994510641a79b136548810a138a11b74c571fcb1","tid":1197380,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"達仔都罷台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"神抽"},{"pid":"03ce10c2043cf2014eae649530c4b2eba135ff00","tid":1197380,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdcf1d1627cf9705ab01b000af788a13472068b","tid":1197380,"uid":254801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"嗰啲大陸閪會擺課再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}